# ─── Server-side (Netlify Functions) ──────────────────────────────────────
# Set these in Netlify → Site settings → Environment variables (NOT committed).
# They are read by the functions in netlify/functions and never reach the browser.

MOONSHOT_API_KEY=sk-...
# Optional — defaults to kimi-k2-0711-chat.
# AI_MODEL=kimi-k2-0711-chat

# ─── Local dev only ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# To test functions locally, put MOONSHOT_API_KEY in a local .env and run:
#   npx netlify dev
# (Plain `npm run dev` serves the UI but NOT the functions.)
